                        "name": "andras",
                        "displayName": "Andras Gyomrey",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Where's the error: docs or implementation? Would a patch be useful?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=andras",
                        "name": "andras",
                        "displayName": "Andras Gyomrey",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-08-15T16:00:12.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-08-15T16:00:12.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/51606",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=yatessc",
                        "name": "yatessc",
                        "displayName": "Simon Yates",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Probably only implementation, depending on the decision as to required behaviour.\r\n\r\nAccording to the documentation at present, in the example I gave above an exception should be thrown for the missing parameter to the username option, but in fact it consumes the -c as the parameter value, and the casenumber option is not set.  This results in incorrect errors - the calling script thinks that the casenumber option has not been set (or passed at all), whereas in fact it is the username that is missing.\r\n\r\nAs I said, the simple solution would be to check the next argument for a leading '-' in the required parameter case as well, just as the optional parameter case already does.  This would enable the code to function as documented.  (It is possible, though I would hope unlikely, that this would break some existing code relying on the undocumented behaviour.)\r\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=yatessc",
                        "name": "yatessc",
                        "displayName": "Simon Yates",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-08-16T09:30:57.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-08-16T09:30:57.000+0000"
                }
            ]
        }
